  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the study is to find out if nocturnal non-invasive ventilation during pulmonary
      rehabilitation increases exercise capacity and quality of life more than pulmonary
      rehabilitation alone.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
